67
00:03:52,190 --> 00:03:54,630
don't dare to offend the Ke family.

68
00:03:55,030 --> 00:03:56,840
It's precisely because
my father was an esteemed figure.

69
00:03:56,960 --> 00:03:58,000
He was honest and upright.

70
