on his face when he left the hall.

110
00:06:09,620 --> 00:06:10,580
According to my deduction,

111
00:06:11,260 --> 00:06:13,380
Grandmother didn't believe
Ji Jingtang's words.

112
00:06:15,680 --> 00:06:16,750
To catch a thief,
you must find the stolen goods.

113
