evidence of his crime.

115
00:06:21,920 --> 00:06:22,800
You're right.

116
00:06:24,830 --> 00:06:26,040
Ji Jingtang was a victim.

117
00:06:26,040 --> 00:06:26,920
But Grandmother didn't believe him.

118
00:06:27,240 --> 00:06:29,270
However, if we bring
the blind old lady here to testify for him,

119
00:06:29,270 --> 00:06:30,480
