of his crime.

120
00:06:30,480 --> 00:06:31,720
Grandmother will believe us by then.

121
00:06:35,360 --> 00:06:36,920
However, that old lady is

122
00:06:36,920 --> 00:06:38,480
in Jiangzhou, which is a distant land.

123
00:06:38,750 --> 00:06:40,000
And, we're stuck in the residence.

124
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:41,160
We can't go anywhere else.

125
00:06:41,830 --> 00:06:42,680
I have an idea.

126
00:06:50,000 --> 00:06:50,720
That's great.

127
00:06:50,720 --> 00:06:51,360
I can go...

128
00:06:53,680 --> 00:06:54,510
