134
00:07:13,800 --> 00:07:14,870
Grandmother, don't worry.

135
00:07:15,270 --> 00:07:16,070
I'm fine.

136
00:07:17,310 --> 00:07:20,560
I'm sure it's because he exhausted himself
a few days ago.

137
00:07:20,750 --> 00:07:22,070
That's why he fell sick.

138
00:07:23,270 --> 00:07:24,000
Grandmother,

139
00:07:24,600 --> 00:07:25,480
I'm fine.

140
00:07:26,190 --> 00:07:27,510
