157
00:08:10,240 --> 00:08:13,430
I'll tell Shizhao to dispatch his men
and send you guys there.

158
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:16,270
Grandmother,

159
00:08:16,680 --> 00:08:17,560
Shizhao still needs

160
00:08:17,560 --> 00:08:18,950
to manage our family business.

161
00:08:19,190 --> 00:08:20,160
He's busy with official affairs.

162
00:08:20,390 --> 00:08:21,720
Don't trouble him.

163
00:08:22,430 --> 00:08:23,480
Everything will be fine

164
00:08:23,630 --> 00:08:25,480
