165
00:08:27,270 --> 00:08:28,160
Bingyan,

166
00:08:28,360 --> 00:08:30,920
I'll entrust Tianlei to your care then.

167
00:08:31,600 --> 00:08:33,200
Grandmother, don't worry.

168
00:08:36,870 --> 00:08:37,750
By the way, Grandmother,

169
00:08:38,790 --> 00:08:41,440
Yansheng was always cooped up
inside her room.

170
00:08:41,670 --> 00:08:43,320
May we bring her there as well?

171
00:08:43,600 --> 00:08:45,360
The house in the forest is
refreshing and quiet.

172
00:08:45,600 --> 00:08:46,600
She can take a breather there.

173
00:08:52,200 --> 00:08:52,790
All right.

174
00:08:53,600 --> 00:08:54,320
All right.

175
00:09:01,440 --> 00:09:02,120
Young Master,

176
00:09:02,840 --> 00:09:05,440
