Are your men reliable?

179
00:09:10,670 --> 00:09:12,390
Don't worry. They're definitely reliable.

180
00:09:23,150 --> 00:09:23,790
Your Ladyship,

181
00:09:24,200 --> 00:09:25,080
that's him.

182
00:09:25,510 --> 00:09:27,440
He's the new wheeler Wang Huzi had hired.

183
00:09:31,510 --> 00:09:32,390
