184
00:09:33,200 --> 00:09:33,840
It's fine.

185
00:09:35,270 --> 00:09:36,200
Let's beat them at their own game.

186
00:09:37,540 --> 00:09:43,140
[Qi Residence]

187
00:09:48,600 --> 00:09:50,270
Xiaoxi, you can leave
with Yansheng first.

188
00:09:50,480 --> 00:09:51,630
Remember to accomplish your task
in East Street.

189
00:09:51,630 --> 00:09:52,550
Be careful.

190
00:09:52,670 --> 00:09:53,200
Yes, Miss.

191
00:10:03,150 --> 00:10:04,670
Head to East Street. Let's depart.

192
00:10:05,120 --> 00:10:05,670
Yes, ma'am.

193
00:10:09,000 --> 00:10:10,120
Let's depart!

194
00:10:28,620 --> 00:10:37,660
[Peace and prosperity]

195
