198
00:11:16,030 --> 00:11:17,840
Third Young Master is lacking some tonics.

199
00:11:17,960 --> 00:11:19,320
I'll buy them from the herb shop.

200
00:11:19,790 --> 00:11:21,630
There might not be any herb shops
near the house.

201
00:11:21,630 --> 00:11:22,960
