206
00:11:41,870 --> 00:11:42,870
Keep an eye on the horse for me.

207
00:11:42,870 --> 00:11:44,200
I need to take a dump.

208
00:11:44,200 --> 00:11:45,200
-I'll return in a second.
-Okay.

209
00:11:45,320 --> 00:11:45,910
You should hurry.

210
00:12:14,380 --> 00:12:15,820
[Qingrun Apothecary]

211
00:12:19,550 --> 00:12:20,150
Take care.

212
00:12:24,270 --> 00:12:25,550
Follow the prescription.

213
00:12:25,550 --> 00:12:27,740
[Prescription]

214
00:12:30,860 --> 00:12:32,500
[Rush to this location in secret.]

215
00:12:38,910 --> 00:12:39,480
