216
00:12:41,030 --> 00:12:41,790
This is what you need.

217
00:12:41,910 --> 00:12:42,550
It'll be five liang.

218
00:12:45,480 --> 00:12:47,030
Here you go. Thank you.

219
00:12:52,540 --> 00:12:55,860
