for recuperation purposes.

230
00:13:54,050 --> 00:13:55,100
Do not interrupt us.

231
00:13:55,810 --> 00:13:57,220
You guys can keep guard outside

232
00:13:57,460 --> 00:13:58,810
and stay in the side chambers.

233
00:13:59,220 --> 00:14:00,220
If anyone disobeys our order,

234
00:14:00,290 --> 00:14:01,530
Third Young Master will report the case

235
00:14:01,860 --> 00:14:03,260
to Grandmother once we head back.

236
00:14:03,930 --> 00:14:04,860
She'll definitely punish you severely

237
00:14:04,860 --> 00:14:06,140
and kick you out of our residence.

238
00:14:06,380 --> 00:14:07,260
Understood?

239
00:14:07,460 --> 00:14:08,140
Understood.

240
00:14:39,140 --> 00:14:40,340
All done. When will we depart?

241
00:14:40,650 --> 00:14:41,930
There's no time better than now.

242
00:14:42,020 --> 00:14:44,650
Let's depart tonight.

243
00:14:45,050 --> 00:14:47,020
Tonight? How?

244
00:14:47,500 --> 00:14:48,690
Master built a secret path

245
00:14:48,930 --> 00:14:50,220
in the house.

246
00:14:52,690 --> 00:14:53,380
Xiaoxi,

247
00:14:53,810 --> 00:14:54,860
you may stay here

248
00:14:55,050 --> 00:14:56,100
and proceed according to our plan.

249
00:14:56,290 --> 00:14:57,340
Understood, Third Young Master.

250
00:15:00,770 --> 00:15:02,170
Buddies, the night shift is tough.

251
00:15:02,530 --> 00:15:03,690
Here's an excellent vat
of Nverhong liquor.

252
00:15:03,980 --> 00:15:04,620
You two should have some.

253
00:15:05,050 --> 00:15:05,770
-But...
-Come on.

254
00:15:06,020 --> 00:15:06,570
But...

255
00:15:06,770 --> 00:15:08,500
We can't drink during our shift.

256
00:15:08,500 --> 00:15:10,170
The night is long.
Having some liquor will ease your boredom.

257
00:15:10,170 --> 00:15:10,980
Here.

258
00:15:10,980 --> 00:15:11,930
You guys can share it.

259
00:15:11,930 --> 00:15:12,460
Come.

260
00:15:13,260 --> 00:15:13,860
Drink up.

261
00:15:13,860 --> 00:15:14,570
Hurry!

262
00:15:16,770 --> 00:15:17,570
Give it to me.

263
00:15:18,290 --> 00:15:20,260
Why is Third Young Master so quiet today?

264
00:15:20,930 --> 00:15:22,020
Give me another sip.

265
00:15:34,380 --> 00:15:35,980
Third Young Master, Third Young Mistress,

266
00:15:36,290 --> 00:15:37,460
would you guys like to have some snacks?

267
00:15:46,620 --> 00:15:47,810
Come, give me a sip.

268
00:15:54,570 --> 00:15:55,690
-Thank you.
-Thanks.

269
00:15:55,860 --> 00:15:56,770
Don't mention it.

270
00:15:56,980 --> 00:15:57,530
Keep up the good work.

271
00:15:57,530 --> 00:15:58,810
Take care.

272
00:16:47,460 --> 00:16:48,460
I didn't expect the house

273
00:16:48,460 --> 00:16:49,650
to have a secret path inside.

274
00:16:49,650 --> 00:16:50,380
